/wrkdirs/overlays/overlay/www/webkit2-gtk/work-40/.build/WTF/Headers/wtf/TypeCasts.h: In instantiation of 'static bool WTF::TypeCastTraits<ExpectedType, ArgType, isBaseType>::isOfType(ArgType&) [with ExpectedType = const WebCore::SVGLinearGradientElement; ArgType = const WebCore::SVGElement; bool isBaseType = false]':
/wrkdirs/overlays/overlay/www/webkit2-gtk/work-40/.build/WTF/Headers/wtf/TypeCasts.h:58:71:   required from 'bool WTF::is(const ArgType&) [with ExpectedType = WebCore::SVGLinearGradientElement; ArgType = WebCore::SVGElement]'
