      |            ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~^~~~~~~~
/wrkdirs/overlays/overlay/www/webkit2-gtk/work-40/.build/WTF/Headers/wtf/TypeCasts.h:120:5:   required from 'WTF::match_constness_t<Source, Target>& WTF::downcast(Source&) [with Target = WebCore::SVGLinearGradientElement; Source = WebCore::SVGElement; match_constness_t<Source, Target> = WebCore::SVGLinearGradientElement]'
