/wrkdirs/overlays/overlay/www/webkit2-gtk/work-40/.build/WTF/Headers/wtf/TypeCasts.h:41:28: note: 'std::is_void_v<const WebCore::SVGLinearGradientElement>' evaluates to false

These apparently resolve on Linux and other platforms. In the meantime there is a private ENABLE_LAYER_BASED_SVG_ENGINE that is enabled for GTK by default, going to try disabling it here.
